OL,3,CThe Wave reopens in time for English
OL,4,CPara Surfing Open
OL,6,FAn inland surfing lake on the
OL,7,Foutskirts of Bristol has been sold to
OL,8,Fnew owners and will reopen in time to
OL,9,Fhost the 2025 English Para Surfing
OL,10,FOpen competition.
OL,12,FThe Wave shut suddenly on Thursday 26
OL,13,FJune, amid what it described as a
OL,14,F"financial technicality."
