OL,3,CThe Wave reopens in time for English
OL,4,CPara Surfing Open
OL,6,FIn a statement that day, majority
OL,7,Fowners Sullivan Street Partners said:
OL,8,F"It is with great sadness that we
OL,9,Fannounce the closure of The Wave
OL,10,FBristol, the UK's first inland surf
OL,11,Fdestination and a much-loved community
OL,12,Fasset"
OL,14,FBut today, Tuesday 1 July, The Wave
OL,15,Fhas reopened under new ownership -
OL,16,Frevealing that it will still host the
OL,17,FEnglish Para Surfing Open competition.
OL,19,FIn a post on Facebook and Instagram on
OL,20,FMonday 30 July, The Wave said: "The
OL,21,Fwaves are ON!!!!
