OL,3,CThe Wave reopens in time for English
OL,4,CPara Surfing Open
OL,6,F"We are so excited to let you all know
OL,7,Fthat we will be reopening our doors at
OL,8,F630 am tomorrow (Tuesday 1 July) and
OL,9,Fall wave sessions will run as
OL,10,Fscheduled.
OL,12,F"Our incredible Wavemaker team has
OL,13,Fpulled together as always and been
OL,14,Fworking flat out to get everything
OL,15,Fback up and running.
