OL,3,CThe Wave reopens in time for English
OL,4,CPara Surfing Open
OL,6,F"This also means that the eagerly
OL,7,Fanticipated English Para Surfing Open
OL,8,Fcompetition will be able to take place
OL,9,Fas planned on 2-3 July - and we can't
OL,10,Fthink of a better way to mark opening
OL,11,Four doors again!
OL,13,F"We want to thank all our wonderful
OL,14,Fcommunity for the outpouring of love
OL,15,Fand support over the last days. It
OL,16,Fmeans so much. See you in the water
OL,17,Fsoon"
